            "text": "A daily affirmation for breaking the chain. Generational money anxiety passes through the things we say and the things we don't say, the flinch at a price, the apology for wanting, the silence when money comes up. This affirmation names the alternative: ease, moved from this generation forward rather than anxiety.",
