        "content": [
          {
            "text": "How to use it",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Say it three times in the morning, hand on heart. Say it again in the moments where the old pattern wants to reassert itself. When you catch yourself saying something about money to your children that you know carries the old anxiety. The affirmation is the redirect, said quietly afterward.",
